This repository contains default http://code.google.com/p/simple-build-tool project for http://circumflex.ru web application.

You can get this skeleton by git clone git://github.com/sassunt/circumflex-sbt-quickstart.git
or download http://github.com/downloads/sassunt/circumflex-sbt-quickstart/circumflex-sbt-quickstart.zip and unzip it.

Quick start.
1. run sbt:
    $ sbt
2. in sbt shell run commands "update" and "container:start"
    > update
    > container:start
3. check out http://localhost:8080 (should be <h1>it works!</h1>)

Also you can make orm stuff in sbt console just like in mvn scala:console
